quran[431]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,Maha beuruekat cit sidroe Tuhan È Nyang Po keurajeuen nyang Maha Luah Bak jaroe Tuhan keurajeuen teutap Kuasa Neuh that hanaban peugah Tuhan kuasa ateuh barangpeue
  67,2,Neupeujeuet dumpeue hana soe bantah Neupeujeuet mate udep pih saban Nyan keuh cubaan Neubri le Allah Neuuji gata soe nyang got amai Soe nyang le beukai di jih jikeubah Tuhan Perkasa Maha Pengampon
  67,3,Langet Neususon tujoh tabaqah Peuneujeut Tuhan hana nyang cacat Watee talihat hana nyang salah Tangieng sigo treuk keunan tapandang Peue na nyang irang hana got ulah
  67,4,Teuma taulang meu dua go treuk Hana meu sineuk taeu nyang salah Jiwoe pandangan mata jisurot Hana nyang karot nyang na meupayah
  67,5,Bak langet nyang toe taeu hiasan Kamoe boh bintang hu meujeureulah Kamoe rhom ngon nyan dum chetan-chetan Nyang daya insan sabe jihilah Teuma keu jih nyan Kamoe seudia Azeub nuraka tutong that leupah
  67,6,Keu kaphe teuma nyang lawan Tuhan Azeub jahannam nuraka juah Sijeuheut teumpat nyan keuh nuraka
  67,7,Meubura-bura apui hu mirah ‘Oh ban ka geutiek awak nyan keunan Jimeusu yoh nyan meubura-bura
  67,8,Sang-sang ka anco apui nuraka Meubura-bura beungeh jih leupah ‘Oh geutiek kon saboh rombongan Geutanyong pakon rhot keunoe dikah Meunan geutanyong le ureueng jaga Peue hana teuka rasul jak bak kah
  67,9,Jikheun na geujak rasul bak kamoe Teuma di kamoe hana meupapah Meukheun sulet that haba gata nyan Hana Neupeutron sapeue le Allah Gata sisat that han kamoe deungo
  67,10,Adak meudeungo teuma jipeugah Adak meudeungo watee nyan keubit Meupike beu got han dumnoe balah Han roh jeut kamoe asoe nuraka
  67,11,Meungaku dacha bandum jih salah Binasa keubit asoe nuraka
  67,12,Nyang laen rupa ureueng meutuah Ureueng nyang takot keu Tuhan gopnyan Bah tan geukalon yo geuh that leupah Ureueng nyan bandum Neuampon dacha Raya that pahla lom han ban peugah
  67,13,Peue nyang tamarit got tarahsia Got tapeunyata takheun ngon babah Bandum Neuteupue Allah Taʻala Peue nyang lam dada Neuteupue sudah
  67,14,Ek han Neuteupue Droeneuh nyang peujeuet Haloh that keubit ‘eleumee Allah Keubit that haloh Neumaklum dumpeue
  67,15,Neupeujeuet bumoe keu tanyoe mudah Beudoh jak laju jeuet lungkiek bumoe Raseuki teuh nyoe sinan Neukeubah Tapajoh laju raseuki gata Dudoe tagisa tawoe bak Allah
  67,16,Ek aman gata bak ureueng langet Neuyue peusinget bumoe le Allah Meuguncang-guncang bumoe ngon gata
  67,17,Ek aman gata lom cuba peugah Batee Neuyue rhom bak ureueng langet ‘Oh keunong teupat mate teuh reubah Tateupue treuk peue nyang Lon peuingat Pakri saket that hanaban peugah
  67,18,Meunan pih kawom dilee nibak jih Han jitem pateh peue nyang peurintah Peue nyang geupeugah jikheun nyan sulet Pakriban saket keu jih Lon balah
  67,19,Peue hana jieu ticem teureubang Jipo lam awan rame jih leupah Meubareh-bareh jipo di ateuh Sayeup jipeulheuh jitop jipeuhah Tuhan nyang theun jih bek rhot u bumoe Neukalon dumpeue bandum le Allah
  67,20,Boh soe nyoe teuma nyang jeuet keu teuntra Nyang tulong gata ‘oh teuka musoh Meunyo kon Tuhan nyang that geumaseh Di kaphe paleh sabe lam salah Bandum si kaphe ka chetan taki
  67,21,Boh soe lom nyang bri bandum napakah Soe bri raseuki teuma keu gata Meunyo Neusangga Neutheun le Allah Tapi jeut mabok cit lom krang ceukang Batat ngon tungang dumpeue jibantah
  67,22,Ureueng jak meugom muka bak tanoh Soe got teuma jih ngon ureueng ceudah Geujak meusigak bak jalan teupat Soe nyang troh siat ho nyang geulangkah
  67,23,"Takheun Tuhan keuh nyang peujeuet gata Dilee phon mula sampoe ‘oh sudah Geulinyueng, mata ngon ate gata Bandum nyan nyata peuneujeuet Allah Tapi tachuko nit that nyang tatem"
  67,24,Takheun lom laen peuneujeuet Allah Neupeujeuet gata rame lam bumoe Meusapat dudoe teuma bak Allah
  67,25,Jitanyong pajan janji nyan teuka Meu beuna gata peue nyang tapeugah
  67,26,Takheun atra nyan ‘eleumee Tuhan Di lon nyoe mantong meu Neuyue peugah Neuyue peuingat bak lon nyoe mantong
  67,27,‘Oh ban jikalon azeub meurimbah Muka si kaphe bandum ka pucat Hana le ubat ka abeh sudah Geukheun lom bak jih nyoe nyang ka lakee Yoh masa dilee beu rijang leupah
  67,28,Takheun boh pakri meunyo lon mate Rakan lon sare pih abeh sudah Got pih di Tuhan Neugaseh kamoe Rahmat keu kamoe Neubri le Allah Soe nyang ek peuglah teuma si kaphe Azeub bukon le peudeh that leupah
  67,29,Takheun leh nyan keuh Tuhan nyang Rahman Kamoe meuiman bandum keu Allah Bandum bak Tuhan tawakai kamoe Tateupue dudoe soe nyang bit salah Soe nyang bit nyata jih nyan lam sisat
  67,30,Takheun leh siat pakri ‘oh susah Watee hana ie ka tho di bumoe Watee nyan bak soe teuma tapeugah Soe bri mata ie teuma keu gata Mangat dum gata tajep puleh grah
  68,1,Nun Peue meukeusud Nun bak awal ayat Tuhan Hadharat hana Neupeugah Demi na kalam ngon nyang jih surat
  68,2,Gata kon meuhat lagee jih peugah Nikmat Po gata gata kon gila
  68,3,Nyang le di gata pahla bak Allah Han peutoh-peutoh pahla keu gata
  68,4,Lom sipheuet gata pih jroh that leupah
  68,5,Dudoe pih taeu jih dum pih jieu
  68,6,Soe nyang bit rabue pungo sileupah
  68,7,Po gata keubit Neuteupue that-that Soe nyang bit sisat jalan ka salah Neuteupue that soe nyang na peutunyok Nyang ka geujak cok jalan got leupah
  68,8,Teuma awak nyan bek roh taseutot Nyang jikheun sulet dum ayat Allah
  68,9,Napsu jih gata meugot-got ngon jih Sang-sang bit di jih got-got that leupah
  68,10,Lom bek taseutot awak hina that Di jih sia-at ka jimeusumpah
  68,11,Tukang peusuna jak keunoe keudeh
  68,12,Atra jeh di jih bek sagai leupah Meunyo buet nyang got di jih kriet jih that Keubit jeuheut that jipubuet salah
  68,13,Keujam jih geuthee laen nibak nyan
  68,14,Areuta jih nyan cit le sileupah Meunan lom aneuk di jih pih le that
  68,15,‘Oh geukheun ayat jipaleng bagah Dum ayat Kamoe jikheun nyan dongeng Kra ureueng jameun bandum jipeugah
  68,16,Kamoe boh tanda ‘oh dudoe keu jih Bak beuralee jih meucap meukeubah
  68,17,Dilee awaknyan ka Kamoe ujoe Lagee meuujoe kawom nyang sudah Sinan na lampoh jih di kawom nyan Teuma watee nyan ka jimeusumpah Singoh ban beungoh tajak pot ase
  68,18,Hana jipike keu gop nyang susah Han sagai jibri keu ureueng gasien
  68,19,Meu troh treuk keunan ureueng ziarah Teungoh teungeut jih ureueng nyan teuka Nibak Po gata sideh geulangkah
  68,20,Jeut treuk lampoh nyan ka lagee arang Ka seupot itam anco dum bicah
  68,21,Jimeuhoi treuk ngon jih dum ‘oh beungoh
  68,22,Bandum tabeudoh jak keudeh bagah Meunyo meunapsu tajak pot ase Bak keubon sare laju talangkah
  68,23,Jijak treuk laju ngon jih meus‘ah-s‘ah
  68,24,Bek leumah-leumah tanyoe jak bagah Ureueng gasien bek jitamong keunoe Tanyoe uroe nyoe tajak pot buah
  68,25,Jijak treuk laju padahai di jih Ek jibri le jih peue-peue nyang mudah
  68,26,‘Oh ban jikalon lampoh lagee nyoe Jikheun bit tanyoe sisat sileupah
  68,27,Tapi di tanyoe han sapeue na le
  68,28,Ureueng got ate teuma kheun bagah Kon ka Lon peugah bak bandum gata Pakon han gata tapujoe Allah Takheun teuseubeh tapujoe Tuhan
  68,29,Jikheun treuk yoh nyan Subhanallah Keubit Po tanyoe Maha Suci that Tanyoe lalem that hanaban peugah
  68,30,Nyang ladom jikheun nyan salah gata Bandum jih teuma peusalah-salah
  68,31,Jikheun ceulaka bandum geutanyoe Sabab geutanyoe leupah that culah
  68,32,Kadang Neutem bri le Po geutanyoe c Laen Neugantoe nyang leubeh ceudah Taharap ampon bak Po geutanyoe
  68,33,Meunan keuh Kamoe azeub meubalah Azeub akhirat raya nibak nyoe Meunyo jiteupue han roe jih salah
  68,34,Ureueng takwa nibak Po gopnyan Churuga naʻim ka lheuh Neukeubah
  68,35,Po kamoe peusa ureueng Iseulam Lagee kaphe nyan nyang pubuet salah
  68,36,Pakriban meunan gata tahukom
  68,37,Lam kitab teuh dum peue na geupeugah Na kitab teuh dum teuma di gata
  68,38,Jeut ban nyang hawa tapileh sudah
  68,39,Peue na meujanji gata ngon Kamoe Sampoe ‘an dudoe taakad sumpah Nyang jeuet gata dum meunan tahukom
  68,40,Tanyong bak jih dum mangat jipeugah Soe keupala jih nyang hukom meunoe
  68,41,Na ngon jih dum nyoe laen jikeubah Jak hai ngon jih dum keunoe tayue ba Meunyo jih beuna peue nyang jipeugah
  68,42,Uroe deuh beuteh bandum ka teulhon Geuyue sujud lom laju beu bagah Han ek sujud le di jih watee nyan
  68,43,Mata ka rabon khuchu‘ that leupah Watee nyan di jih hina ngon malee Yoh geuyue dilee han jitem papah Yoh mantong teuga han jitem pubuet ‘Oh geuyue sujud di jih jibantah
  68,44,Bah jih deungon Lon jinoe meuhukom Jikheun narit Lon sulet that leupah Lon keumeung hoi jih dum seun-seun bacut Bah le jipubuet laju nyang salah Hana jiteupue ho jikeumeung bloh
  68,45,Jih Lon bri tanggoh yoh goh Lon balah 7 Leubeh carong Lon roe bak teumaki
  68,46,Peue na tayue bri keu gata upah Jeut jih nyan teuma geuhon ngon utang
  68,47,Peue na bak jih nyan ‘eleumee Allah s ‘Eleumee gaeb nyang tan gop teupue Jituleh dumpeue beuna ngon salah
  68,48,Teuma tasaba hukom Po gata Bek lagee haba masa nyang sudah 5 Lagee soe dilee dalam pruet eungkot Sang-sang teumakot geuba peurintah Geulakee duʻa gopnyan di laot Kawom buet karot beungeh geuh leupah
  68,49,Adak kon nikmat bak Tuhan gopnyan Teutiek geuh sinan dalam blang luah Meuhat jicaci bandum buet gopnyan
  68,50,Lan pih di Tuhan gopnyan Neupeuglah Neupileh gopnyan keu ureueng saleh d Ureueng nyang leubeh geunaseh Allah
  68,51,Kaphe ‘oh jingieng sang ateuh gata Jikeuih gata sinan beureubah ‘Oh ban jideungo dike tabaca Keubit ka gila gata jipeugah
  68,52,Padahai Ziker haba peuingat s Le bandum umat jitueng phaedah Keu bandum alam jeuet keu peuingat r Soe nyang tem ingat nyang nyang meutuah
  69,1,Meuteuntee that-that han jeut han teuka
  69,2,Peue roe nyang teuka meuteuntee leupah
  69,3,Na tateupue nyang han jeuet han teuka
  69,4,Yoh dilee masa Tsamud geupeugah Jikheun sulet that uroe kiamat Meunan pih si ‘Ad jikheun beurakah
  69,5,Tsamud binasa ngon bala hebat
  69,6,Binasa si ‘Ad angen kreuh leupah Angen sijuek that badei ngon tophan
  69,7,Tujoh malam tan jipiyoh payah Jeuet lom meutamah ngon lapan uroe Kawom teupipoe taeu dum reubah Sang bak kureuma nyang ka brok asoe Reubah sinaroe abeh dum tewah
  69,8,Hana nyang tinggai jih le meusidroe
  69,9,Peuraʻun pande pih hana ubah Yoh goh Peuraʻun ngon muktafikat Bandum saban that jipubuet salah
  69,10,Jimaksiet dum jih rasul tuhan jih Neusiksa treuk jih nyang brat sileupah
  69,11,‘Oh teuka tophan jiek ie raya Gata lam bahtra dum Kamoe keubah
  69,12,Meupeujeuet nyan dum jeuet keu peuingat Keu gata meuhat tatueng phaedah Geulinyueng nyang got sabe jiingat
  69,13,‘Oh jan kiamat teuma geupeugah Geuyup beuragoe sigo yup meuhat
  69,14,Bumoe geuangkat ngon gunong meugah Bumoe ngon gunong meuseumpom anco
  69,15,Uroe nyan baro kiamat sudah
  69,16,Langet pih bicah uroe nyan reului Hana daya le leumoh jih leupah
  69,17,Jeut sagoe langet dum malaikat Arasy Hadharat geume dum sudah Lapan droe ureueng nyang me ‘arasy nyan Di ateuh gopnyan sinan keuh ‘arasy
  69,18,Uroe nyan gata geuba bak Tuhan Meu sapeue pih tan meusom bak Allah
  69,19,Soe nyang cok kitab ngon jaroe uneun Geujok rot uneun jikheun treuk bagah Beudoh dum jak kheun kitab lon nyopat
  69,20,Yoh dilee meuhat lon yakin sudah Lon yakin di lon akan geuhisab
  69,21,Ureueng nyan meuhat seunang that leupah Udep that seunang rila Hadharat
  69,22,Meuteumeung teumpat churuga indah Dalam churuga nyang manyang that-that
  69,23,Boh kayee le that miyup sileupah
  69,24,Tapajoh tajep seunang ngon ladat Sabab buet got that masa nyang sudah
  69,25,Soe-soe nyang geujok rot wie jih kitab Jikheun treuk ligat meunyesai leupah Adak jeuet di lon bek geujok kitab
  69,26,Bek lon eu hisab keu lon geupeugah
  69,27,Nyang got cit mate mantong bek meunoe Mangat atra nyoe dum abeh sudah
  69,28,Areuta lon le hana guna le
  69,29,Kuasa han le anco dum bicah
  69,30,Rante bak takue jih taboh laju
  69,31,Dalam apui hu tatiek jih bagah
  69,32,Lheuh nyan tarante jih lom di sinan Panyang rante nyan na tujoh ploh hah
  69,33,Han jimeuiman di jih keu Tuhan Allah keuh Tuhan nyang agong leupah
  69,34,Han jitem yue bri di jih makanan Keu ureueng gasien nyang dalam susah
  69,35,Uroe nyoe di jih hana ngon jih le
  69,36,Makanan geubri nanoh ngon darah
  69,37,Nyan keuh makanan ureueng meudacha Geubri nyan saja keu ureueng salah
  69,38,Ulon meusumpah ngon peue nyang taeu
  69,39,Nyang hana taeu pih saban leupah
  69,40,Keubit nyan narit rasul mulia Atra nyan geuba Neuyue le Allah
  69,41,Bukon nyan narit ureueng meupanton Gata meuiman nit that sileupah
  69,42,Jeuet keu peuingat di gata pih nit Tapi kon narit ureueng meurajah
  69,43,Tron nibak Tuhan Po bandum alam
  69,44,Meunyo buet gopnyan lagee tapeugah Geupeuna-peuna narit ateuh Lon
  69,45,Teuntee Lon hukom gopnyan le bagah Bak jaroe uneun lon mat geuh lon hue
  69,46,Lon koh bak takue sinan le reubah
  69,47,Lam kawan gata hana meusidroe Nyang peutheun geuh nyoe bek Kamoe balah
  69,48,Atra nyan cit roe haba peuingat Keu ureueng nyang that takwa keu Allah
  69,49,Kamoe meuteupue lam kawan gata Na nyang duseuta gopnyan jipeugah
  69,50,Teuma atra nyan keu awak kaphe Meuhat jeuet ase meunyesai teulah
  69,51,Atra nyan beuna cit hak tayakin
  69,52,Teuseubeh takheun tapujoe Allah Takheun teuseubeh ngon nan Po gata Nyang Maha Raya Agong ngon Meugah
  70,1,Na jilakee le ureueng meulakee Beu teuka teuntee azeub beu bagah
  70,2,Azeub keu kaphe han ek soe sangka
  70,3,Atra nyan sigra Neubri le Allah Tuhan keuh nyang Po dum tingkat-tingkat
  70,4,Rot malaikat dum ek bak Allah Deungon Jibaril pih geujak sajan Siuroe keunan bandum geulangkah Limong ploh ribee thon kada uroe Meu tajak keudroe jeuet trep sileupah
  70,5,Teuma na saba nyang beu jroh that-that
  70,6,Di jih jilihat sang jioh leupah
  70,7,Kamoe meukalon atra nyoe toe that
  70,8,Uroe nyan langet anco dum bicah Lagee dhoi pirak langet sinaroe
  70,9,Gunong pih meunan gapeuh sang ulah
  70,10,Hana soe tanyong ho ngon ho rakan
  70,11,Na geupeukalon sinan dum leupah p Awak nyang salah jitem teuboh droe b Jijok aneuk droe bandum keu upah
  70,12,Jijok peurumoh ngon chedara jih
  70,13,Ngon nyang hiroe jih masa nyang sudah
  70,14,Lom bandum ureueng nyang na di bumoe Asai jih sidroe geutem peuleupah Dumnan uroe nyan azeub saket that
  70,15,Keubit nyan teumpat nuraka juah
  70,16,Apui nuraka phon jilpluek kulet
  70,17,Jipreh geuintat ureueng nyang salah Meunyo buet nyang got sit jipeulikot Di jih peuturot napsu seurakah
  70,18,Dumna areuta ka jipeusapat Jikeubah got that han jinapakah
  70,19,Tuhan Neupeujeuet manusia nyoe Malam ngon uroe sabe geulisah
  70,20,‘Oh teuka nyang brok susah jih that-that
  70,21,Meu teuka nyang got kriet jih sileupah
  70,22,Meulengkan ureueng nyang na seumbahyang
  70,23,Sabe seumbahyang han tom geukeubah
  70,24,Bak atra gopnyan hak cit ka teuntee
  70,25,Ureueng meulakee nyang tan napakah Got nyang gasien that hana meulakee
  70,26,Jipateh teuntee lom peue geupeugah Jipateh bit na uroe kiamat
  70,27,Lom pih keu azeub yo jih that leupah
  70,28,Jiteupue keubit azeub Po jih nyan Han ek jih aman droejih jipeuglah
  70,29,Meunan pih ureueng jaga meunalee
  70,30,"Meulengkan teuntee inong jih nyang sah Atawa namiet nyang milek droejih Meunyo nyan di jih han jeut keu: salah"
  70,31,Meunyo ngon laen nyan salah raya
  70,32,Amanah teuma han tom jiubah Meunan pih han tom meuiseuk janji
  70,33,Lom jiek saksi ade sileupah
  70,34,Lom seumbahyang jih that jiplihara Bek na nyang cupa meubacut salah
  70,35,Nyan keuh ureueng nyan asoe churuga Neupeumulia geuh that le Allah
  70,36,Peue dum si kaphe jijak bak gata Peunteng that haba mehmoh jih leupah
  70,37,Rot uneun rot wie meutumpok-tumpok
  70,38,Meuhʻeut jih geujok churuga indah Bak geupeutamong jih lam churuga Nikmat churuga hanaban peugah
  70,39,Han geupeutamong jih dum nyan keunan Meupeujeuet jih nyan ka trang sileupah Di jih jiteupue Kamoe peujeuet jih
  70,40,Di lon nyan keu jih Ulon meusumpah Ulon meusumpah demi Hadharat Timu ngon barat sit milek Allah Keubit roe Kamoe kuasa that-that
  70,41,Meugantoe siat bandum jih bagah y Ngon kawom laen meugantoe dum jih Nyang got nibak jih seumateh leupah r Han ek roe di jih peutalo Kamoe
  70,42,Bah le jih meunoe bek le tapapah Bah le jih mabok jimeuen-meuen Sampoe meuteumeung peue nyang tapeugah Sampoe troh uroe tajanji keu jih
  70,43,Uroe nyan dum jih jibeudoh bagah Teubiet lam uruek beudoh dum rata Sang bak berhala jimeung meulangkah
  70,44,Bandum meuteukui ule jih u yup Mata jih teutop khuchu“ sileupah Han jijeut kalon uwie ngon uneuen š Hina jih yoh nyan hanaban peugah h Uroe nyan keuh nyang dilee geujanji Bandum jih geubri peueu nyang geubalah k
  71,1,Kamoe kirem Noh bak kawom gopnyan Peuingat jih nyan bek pubuet salah Yoh gohlom teuka azeub peudeh that
  71,2,Geukheun treuk ligat kawom meutuah Lon nyoe bak gata Neuyue peuingat Uleh Hadharat nyata Neupeugah
  71,3,Taseumah Allah lom tatakwa Keu Tuhan gata nyang Maha Murah Tataʻat keu Lon bek tameudawa
  71,4,Ampon keu gata Neubri le Allah Neuampon dacha ngon panyang umu Leubeh sigitu bek rijang leupah Dang-dang troh ajai nyang ka meuteuntee Meu ka troh watee han jeuet meu minah Han jeuet le tanggoh meu ka troh watee Meu na ‘eleumee tateupue sudah
  71,5,Geukheun Tuhanku pakri kawomlon Ka Iheuh dum di lon sabe lon peugah Malam ngon uroe lon yue pubuet got
  71,6,Di jih lagee sot hana jipapah Nyang na sit jiplueng leubeh nibak sot
  71,7,‘Oh lon yue nyang got jikheun beurakah Ngon aneuk jaroe jih di geulinyueng Jimeukeuleubong ngon ija sihah Hana jipiyoh jipubuet jeuheut Ngon mbong jih pih that teukabo leupah
  71,8,Teuma lon peugah han le lon som-som Di keu jih bandum lon bri peurintah
  71,9,Lheuh nyan lon lahe kadang pih lon som Jideungo han lom peue nyang lon peugah
  71,10,Talakee ampon lon kheun bak Tuhan f Neuampon rijang gata le Allah
  71,11,Neubri ngon ujeuen keu gata le that
  71,12,Areuta le that Neubri meulimpah Neubri le aneuk teuh lom ngon keubon Neubri deungon krueng seunang teuh leupah
  71,13,Pakon han tatem harap keu Tuhan Deungon adab sopan tapujoe Allah
  71,14,Neupeujeut gata meutingkat-tingkat Di phon bacut that sampoe ‘an sudah
  71,15,Peue hana taeu nyang Tuhan peujeuet Langet Neupeujeuet tujoh tabaqah
  71,16,Neupeujeuet buleuen cahya seureuloe . Ngon mata uroe hu meujeureulah
  71,17,Tuhan peutimoh gata di bumoe
  71,18,Gata Neupeuwoe teuma lom sudah Dudoe Neubangket bandum sinaroe
  71,19,Neupeujeuet bumoe teuleueng ngon luah
  71,20,Mangat jeuet tajak sinan ho nyang hʻeut Peue nyang meukeusud tamita bagah
  71,21,Wahe Tuhanku le Noh lom geukheun Han jipeureumeun peue nyang lon peugah Jimaksiet keu lon di jih jiikot Ureueng nyang karot nyang ba bak salah Atra ngon aneuk jih jeuet keu rugoe Jiturot jih nyoe peue nyang jipeugah
  71,22,Jipubuet jeuheut raya han bagoe
  71,23,Jikheun Tuhan nyoe bandum taseumah Tuhan gata dum waddan suwaʻan Yaghus pih meunan han jeuet takeubah Yaʻuq ngon nasar Tuhan teuh bandum Jipeusisat dum rame sileupah Awak nyang lalem nyang elanya that
  71,24,Bandum ka sisat meutamah-tamah
  71,25,Geupeukaram jih dalam buet jeuheut Jitamong meuhat lam apui mirah À Dalam nuraka bandum jitamong Hana soe tulong meunyo kon Allah
