  77,34,Uroe nyan teuma ceulaka keubit Ureueng kheun sulet keu rasul Allah
  77,35,Jih dum uroe nyoe han jeut marit le
  77,36,Han geuizin le meungaku salah
  77,37,Uroe nyan teuma ceulaka keubit Ureueng kheun sulet keu rasul Allah
  77,38,Nyoe keuh uroe nyoe uroe putosan Ngon gata bandum meusapat sudah Ngon ureueng dilee bandum meusapat
  77,39,Peue ek na pakat Lon nyoe tahilah
  77,40,Uroe nyoe teuma ceulaka keubit Ureueng kheun sulet keu rasul Allah
  77,41,Ureueng takwa lam reului sabe Mata ie ile hana peue peugah
  77,42,Ngon boh kayee le peue nyang geumeuh‘eut
  77,43,Pajoh ngon tajep ladat sileupah Nyan keuh balasan peue nyang tapubuet
  77,44,Soe nyang pubuet got meunan meubalah
  77,45,Uroe nyan teuma ceulaka keubit Ureueng kheun sulet keu rasul Allah
  77,46,Pajoh ngon seunang gata dum siat Tapubuet jeuheut raya that salah
  77,47,Uroe nyan teuma ceulaka keubit Ureueng kheun sulet keu rasul Allah
  77,48,‘Oh geuyue ruku‘ geuyue seumbahyang Jipaleng rijang hana jipapah
  77,49,Uroe nyan teuma ceulaka keubit Ureueng kheun sulet keu rasul Allah
  77,50,Seupoe cit narit nyang jimeuiman Meu han jiiman keu narit Allah